Info.Title: Finders Keepers
Info.Writer: Jeffrey Schenck (story), Peter Sullivan (screenplay), Peter Sullivan (story)
Info.Actors: Jaime Pressly, Patrick Muldoon, Tobin Bell, Marina Sirtis
Info.Plot: A divorced mother of one is thrown into turmoil when her young daughter becomes obsessed with an evil doll left behind by the previous occupants of their new home.
